OL,3,CMan admits killing pensioner on
OL,4,Cmobility scooter in 'motiveless attack'
OL,6,FA man has admitted killing an elderly
OL,7,Fmobility scooter rider in a
OL,8,F"motiveless" knife attack five days
OL,9,Fafter being released from prison.
OL,11,FLee Byer stabbed 87-year-old Thomas
OL,12,FO'Halloran in the neck and chest in
OL,13,FGreenford, west London, in August 2022.
OL,15,FIt can now be reported that Byer had a
OL,16,Fstring of previous convictions, and
OL,17,Fdays earlier had been released from
OL,18,FWormwood Scrubs.
