OL,3,CMan admits killing pensioner on
OL,4,Cmobility scooter in 'motiveless attack'
OL,6,FOn Monday, the 45-year-old, of no
OL,7,Ffixed address, denied murder but
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to the lesser offence
OL,9,Fof manslaughter by diminished
OL,10,Fresponsibility and having an offensive
OL,11,Fweapon.
OL,13,FProsecutor Gareth Patterson KC
OL,14,Faccepted the pleas after mental health
OL,15,Freports found Byer was psychotic,
OL,16,Fhearing voices, suffering from
OL,17,Fparanoid delusions and paranoid
OL,18,Fschizophrenia.
