OL,3,CMan admits killing pensioner on
OL,4,Cmobility scooter in 'motiveless attack'
OL,6,FHe said the defendant's mental state
OL,7,Fprovided an explanation for what was a
OL,8,F"motiveless attack".
OL,10,FGrandfather Mr O'Halloran was
OL,11,Foriginally from Co Clare in western
OL,12,FIreland and had been well known in the
OL,13,Flocal community.
OL,15,FHe was said to be a passionate
OL,16,Fmusician and described as "very
OL,17,Fpopular" in Greenford, often busking
OL,18,Ffor charity.
