OL,3,CMan admits killing pensioner on
OL,4,Cmobility scooter in 'motiveless attack'
OL,6,FFootage on social media showed him
OL,7,Fbusking to raise money for Ukraine
OL,8,Fmonths before the killing.
OL,10,FShortly after 4pm on August 16, 2022,
OL,11,Fpolice received a 999 call from a
OL,12,Fmember of the public who found the
OL,13,Fvictim on his scooter coming from a
OL,14,Fpassageway that runs between
OL,15,FRunneymede Gardens and Welland Gardens.
OL,17,FMr O'Halloran was able to tell the
OL,18,Fpasser-by he had been stabbed,
OL,19,Falthough wounds to his body were
OL,20,Fclearly visible, the Old Bailey has
OL,21,Fpreviously heard.
