OL,3,CMan admits killing pensioner on
OL,4,Cmobility scooter in 'motiveless attack'
OL,6,FThe police arrived within minutes and
OL,7,FMr O'Halloran had collapsed and was
OL,8,Fbeing helped by members of the public.
OL,10,FPolice and medics took over first aid
OL,11,Fbut he was pronounced dead at the
OL,12,Fscene at 4.54pm.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination found he had
OL,15,Fsuffered multiple stab wounds to the
OL,16,Fneck, chest and abdomen.
OL,18,FMr O'Halloran and the defendant were
OL,19,Fcaught on CCTV heading towards the
OL,20,Fpassageway where their paths crossed.
