OL,6,FThe footage showed, apart from Byer,
OL,7,Fno-one else went into or out of the
OL,8,Farea when the victim was attacked.
OL,10,FWhen he left the passageway, a knife
OL,11,Fcould be seen in Byer's hand.
OL,13,FHe was caught on camera depositing a
OL,14,Fknife handle in a drain in Haymill
OL,15,FClose on the way back to his mother's
OL,16,Fhouse.
OL,18,FForensic analysis found the victim's
OL,19,Fblood on the handle, although the
OL,20,Fblade was never found.
