OL,3,CMan admits killing pensioner on
OL,4,Cmobility scooter in 'motiveless attack'
OL,6,FAfter CCTV images of the suspect were
OL,7,Freleased in the media, Byer was
OL,8,Fidentified by people working in the
OL,9,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,11,FAfter being arrested at his mother's
OL,12,Fhouse on August 18, Byer told police:
OL,13,F"Murder, I was in prison at the time."
OL,15,FClothes matching those seen on CCTV
OL,16,Fwere found in a search of the property
OL,17,Fas well as a knife set with handles
OL,18,Fsimilar to the one found in the drain.
