OL,6,FPolice also alleged Byer had tried to
OL,7,Fburn the clothes he was wearing in his
OL,8,Fmother's garden.
OL,10,FIn police interviews, he denied being
OL,11,Fthe suspect caught on CCTV, claiming
OL,12,Fhe was in his mother's garden or the
OL,13,Fpark at the time.
OL,15,FIt can now be reported that Byer had
OL,16,F15 previous convictions recorded
OL,17,Fagainst him for 30 offences dating
OL,18,Fback to when he was 14.
