OL,6,FIn 2011, he was convicted of robbery
OL,7,Fand was sentenced to 12 years in
OL,8,Fprison.
OL,10,FOn August 11, 2022, Byer had been
OL,11,Freleased from Wormwood Scrubs.
OL,13,FMr O'Halloran was survived by his
OL,14,Ffamily, including his sister, two
OL,15,Fbrothers, nieces and nephews.
