OL,3,CMan admits killing pensioner on
OL,4,Cmobility scooter in 'motiveless attack'
OL,6,FAt the time of his death, Fine Gael
OL,7,Fsenator Martin Conway said Mr
OL,8,FO'Halloran visited Ireland regularly
OL,9,Fand that his death had left his home
OL,10,Fcommunity in Ennistymon in "deep shock
OL,11,Fand sadness".
OL,13,F"Tommy, as he was known, left
OL,14,FEnnistymon for London 71 years ago but
OL,15,Ftravelled home almost every year until
OL,16,Fabout 10 years ago," he said.
OL,18,FOld Bailey Judge Mark Lucraft
OL,19,Fadjourned sentencing until May 10.
